headline: This Biotech Stock Eyes Fresh Entry With 522% Earnings Growth Seen

headline: Bull of the Day: Eli Lilly (LLY)
summary: Eli Lilly has solidified itself as a global pharma titan. With leading drugs and a massive obesity market, Lilly is poised to be a juggernaut for years to come.
